# Task 1: Basic Configuration

R1

interface Loopback10
 description R1’s Loopback 10
 ip address 10.10.10.1 255.255.255.255
!
interface GigabitEthernet1/0
 description Connected to R3 Gi1/0  ip address 100.100.13.1 255.255.255.0  no shutdown
!
interface GigabitEthernet2/0
 description Connected to R2 Gi2/0  ip address 100.100.12.1 255.255.255.0  no shutdown


